# ===== LIVE SITE =====
# Coming Soon mode disabled on 2026-04-23. All routes publicly accessible.
# Cloudflare Pages handles clean-URL .html routing automatically — no rewrites needed here.

# Genki QR box landing (2026-05-15) — the QR-printable URL is
# https://www.genki.bg/box/[CODE]. Cloudflare Pages Functions are not
# enabled for this project (verified via a temporary probe), so the
# functions/ approach was abandoned and `_redirects` 200-rewrites get
# overridden by Pages' auto clean-URL normalisation.
#
# Workaround: 301-redirect /box/:code → /box-landing?code=:code. The QR
# stays short and pretty; after the redirect the browser bar shows
# /box-landing?code=… (the page JS reads ?code= from window.location.search).
# A code-less /box visit still lands on the same page.
/box/:code   /box-landing?code=:code   301
/box         /box-landing              301
